Company Overview of Triton Pacific Investment Corporation, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Triton Pacific Investment Corporation, Inc. is a business development company specializing in debt and equity securities of lower middle market companies. The firm prefers to invest in private equity through buyout, structured equity/debt, mezzanine debt investments. It considers minimum investment of $5,000 per individual with additional purchases. The firm prefers to invest in companies with minimum of $70,000 annual income and $70,000 of net worth; or $250,000 of net worth. The firm typically has  a holding period of 5 to 7 years. Triton Pacific Investment Corporation, Inc. is based in Los Angeles, California with an additional offices in Laguna Niguel, California and Richmond, Virginia.


10877 Wilshire Boulevard12th FloorLos Angeles, CA 90024United States



