Triton Pacific Investment Corp., Inc.



 OVERVIEW



Date Founded


2011




Headquarters


10877 Wilshire Boulevard, 12th Floor, Los Angeles, CA 90024




Industries


Trusts & Funds

Private Equity & Venture Capital

Investment Services & Portfolio Management




Company Description


Triton Pacific Investment Corp., Inc. is a non-traded business development company with revenues of $10 - $250 million and EBITDA between $1 - $25 million that seeks investment opportunities in small to mid-sized private companies located in the US. The fund targets companies operating in the fields of healthcare services, software and IT, business services, consumer products, specialty finance, light manufacturing, logistics and value-added distribution. It acquires controlling stakes and provides financing in the form of senior secured and unsecured debt, mezzanine debt, preferred equity, common equity, warrants and other instruments with an investment size ranging from $0.25 - $25 million per portfolio. It also makes investments in secondary market transactions, including equity purchased from current owners and loans acquired from banks, other specialty finance companies, private equity sponsors, loan syndications and other investors.




Website


http://www.tritonpacificbdc.com






